{"tid":2090090,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"驚移民生存唔到個班人係咪寧願入集中營？","createTime":"2020-07-02T03:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T20:44:06.000Z","uid":56546,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f7bb301e882da88c99073f019387641fb5cafd72","tid":2090090,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T03:57:58.000Z","msg":"先唔好話咩海外建國, 定留係度奮戰到最後呢啲咁大義嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n退一步自私啲諗<br />\n人地開到口俾你班人難民身份入<br />\n基本上已經等同無條件咁濟<br />\n老實講英文都唔識個班人, 都唔見得係咩中產或有錢階級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身已經係地底泥,<br />\n你地覺得自己係香港生存, 會過得好過外國？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都要驚一餐, 5年後入集中營死咗都真係唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"7ffedc9487dff87f8e96d16e09c9226724880997","tid":2090090,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1508fa0dae2398cefdf39231743687efba6a41f7","tid":2090090,"uid":33437,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"睇睇193x德國歷史，<br />\n194x之後東德/柏林。<br />\n<br />\n自由只會愈黎愈少，<br />\n最後想走時，<br />\n就太遲了。<br />\n<br />\n咩年齡有機會都應該走左先。"},{"pid":"aeb0a8d9a4a4a489f172496329b68940700cbab7","tid":2090090,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:46:54.000Z","msg":"唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"983414598055bcb56b5ddc992b7d7e06a19f3d3d","tid":2090090,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1508fa0dae2398cefdf39231743687efba6a41f7","tid":2090090,"uid":33437,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"睇睇193x德國歷史，<br />\n194x之後東德/柏林。<br />\n<br />\n自由只會愈黎愈少，<br />\n最後想走時，<br />\n就太遲了。<br />\n<br />\n咩年齡有機會都應該走左先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"留返條命<br />\n共產黨終有一日要倒下"},{"pid":"7f8d663fcdd4aaa2fbf4f349a3877a65d4a0a0fc","tid":2090090,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"睇返中共歷史，下一步係搞大規模清算，奪取社會控制權"},{"pid":"fe93dd